      <txt crct="94" c="X">By using gloves when practical, and being observant of the risk</txt>
      <txt crct="38" c="X">By never touching anything with your hands and always using some kind of tool</txt>
      <txt crct="95" c="X">It depends on the work requirement.</txt>
